_text = "After lunch we decided to go swimming. I took my film camera out on the paddleboard to capture this image.\n\nWe spent that afternoon diving for rocks, and swimming around the lake. We were the only campers in the area, so we quite literally had the entire lake to ourselves.\n\nI could scream out into the wilderness and no one would hear me. We blasted music, danced around and pushed each other into the water. The day was ours, and no one else was there to experience it."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, FriendsLakeTextRoom2, FriendsLakeTextRoom2, false)
